signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Ballcarriers with this ability have faster juke animations.
The most effective ball carriers prioritize maintaining possession over all else. When they enter the zone, no tackles made against them will result in a fumble.
Ballcarriers with this ability will break almost any hit-stick tackle attempts made on them.
Ballcarriers with this ability receive better blocking on pitch, toss, and counter plays.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: For great quarterbacks, vision and anticipation are paramount. When they enter the zone, their first open receiver is highlighted (while they're standing in the pocket).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws inside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all unpressured throws while their feet are set in the pocket (except on high/low throws).
When playing at home, players with this ability can easily enter the Zone.
Passers with this ability have access to four extra hot routes during pre-play adjustments.
True legendary receivers make the impossible possible. When they enter the zone, they have greatly increased success rate on aggressive catches of 50+ yards regardless of coverage.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running post and corner routes.
True legendary receivers make the impossible possible. When they enter the zone, they have greatly increased success rate on aggressive catches of 50+ yards regardless of coverage.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Elite pass rushers are a mix of strength, speed, and tenacity. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their win rate and block shed speed against one-on-one pass blocks.
